(Executive answer: The latest official dataset identified for electric vehicle charging stations is "Belib' - Points de recharge pour véhicules électriques - Disponibilité temps réel", provided by the City of Paris. This dataset offers real-time availability information for charging points within Paris, with the latest update visible in the analyzed sample being 2025-09-25. It contains 2182 rows of data, covering a time span from 2022-06-13 to 2025-09-25. The charging point statuses observed include "Disponible" \(1113 points\), "Occupé \(en charge\)" \(845 points\), "Inconnu" \(161 points\), "En maintenance" \(50 points\), and "Mise en service planifiée" \(13 points\).) Tj
